---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout pageTitle="My Work — Dana Sandy">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-ghost">Work</div>
    <p class="hero-label">Purpose-Driven Product Work</p>
    <h1 class="hero-name">My <em>Work</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Building products and partnerships that serve communities, strengthen organizations, and create lasting impact.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- GOLD DIVIDER -->
  <svg class="gold-divider" viewBox="0 0 1440 48" preserveAspectRatio="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
    <line x1="72" y1="24" x2="400" y2="24" stroke="rgba(200,164,90,0.4)" stroke-width="0.75"/>
    <circle cx="400" cy="24" r="2.5" fill="none" stroke="rgba(200,164,90,0.5)" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="406" y1="24" x2="700" y2="24" stroke="rgba(200,164,90,0.2)" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-dasharray="4 6"/>
    <circle cx="700" cy="24" r="1.5" fill="rgba(200,164,90,0.4)"/>
    <line x1="706" y1="24" x2="1040" y2="24" stroke="rgba(200,164,90,0.2)" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-dasharray="4 6"/>
    <circle cx="1040" cy="24" r="2.5" fill="none" stroke="rgba(200,164,90,0.5)" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="1046" y1="24" x2="1370" y2="24" stroke="rgba(200,164,90,0.4)" stroke-width="0.75"/>
  </svg>

  <!-- CHAPTER 01 — SERVE513 -->
  <article class="chapter reveal" data-chapter="01">
    <div class="chapter-head">
      <span class="chapter-num">01</span>
      <p class="chapter-eyebrow">Case Study · Community Tech · HMIS Application</p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="chapter-title">SERVE<em>513</em></h2>
    <p class="chapter-hook">Volunteers were burning out. Clients were waiting too long. The systems meant to help were getting in the way — so I built something better.</p>

    <hr class="chapter-rule" />

    <div class="chapter-metrics">
      <div class="metric metric-stat" id="s1">
        <span class="metric-val cs-num" id="n1">0%</span>
        <div class="metric-ba">
          <span class="metric-ba-old">45 min</span>
          <span class="metric-ba-arrow">&rarr;</span>
          <span class="metric-ba-new">under 10 min</span>
        </div>
        <span class="metric-lbl">Clothing wait time reduction</span>
        <span class="metric-context">Waitlists at shelters can last all day — every minute saved matters</span>
      </div>
      <div class="metric metric-stat" id="s2">
        <span class="metric-val cs-num" id="n2">0%</span>
        <div class="metric-ba metric-ba-spacer"></div>
        <span class="metric-lbl">Volunteer adoption rate</span>
        <span class="metric-context">No training overhead — volunteers used it under real event pressure</span>
      </div>
      <div class="metric metric-stat" id="s3">
        <span class="metric-val cs-num" id="n3">0%</span>
        <div class="metric-ba">
          <span class="metric-ba-old">23</span>
          <span class="metric-ba-arrow">&rarr;</span>
          <span class="metric-ba-new">27 showers</span>
        </div>
        <span class="metric-lbl">More shower capacity</span>
        <span class="metric-context">Hygiene access is a direct barrier to employment and housing stability</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a class="chapter-read" href="/work/serve513">Read the case study &rarr;</a>
  </article>

  <!-- CHAPTER BREAK -->
  <div class="chapter-break" aria-hidden="true">
    <span></span><span class="dot"></span><span></span>
  </div>

  <!-- CHAPTER 02 — THE PLAYGROUND -->
  <article class="chapter reveal" data-chapter="02">
    <div class="chapter-head">
      <span class="chapter-num">02</span>
      <p class="chapter-eyebrow">Case Study · Newly Shipped · Design + Engineering + Product</p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="chapter-title">The <em>Playground</em></h2>
    <p class="chapter-hook">Testing prototypes shouldn't require a platform. I didn't want integrations, accounts, or setup overhead — I just wanted three steps: upload, share, review. So I built that.</p>

    <hr class="chapter-rule" />

    <div class="chapter-metrics">
      <div class="metric metric-stat">
        <span class="metric-val">Solo</span>
        <span class="metric-lbl">Design · Engineering · Product</span>
        <span class="metric-context">One person, start to ship — the range was the point</span>
      </div>
      <div class="metric metric-stat">
        <span class="metric-val">4 days</span>
        <span class="metric-lbl">Blank repo to live tool</span>
        <span class="metric-context">The short timeline shaped every decision</span>
      </div>
      <div class="metric metric-stat">
        <span class="metric-val">Live</span>
        <span class="metric-lbl">React · Netlify · Clarity</span>
        <span class="metric-context">Newly shipped — report section shows sample data, real tests pending</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a class="chapter-read" href="/work/the-playground/">Read the case study &rarr;</a>

    <p class="chapter-aside">
      <span class="chapter-aside-eyebrow">Part 01 of the SKAI Series</span>
      <a class="chapter-aside-link" href="/posts/playground-part-1">The problem that led to The Playground &rarr;</a>
    </p>
  </article>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="work-cta-section reveal">
    <p class="cta-label">Interested in Working Together?</p>
    <h2 class="cta-heading">Let's build something <em>meaningful</em>.</h2>
    <a href="/contact" class="work-cta">Get in touch &rarr;</a>
  </section>

</Layout>

<script>
  function countUp(el, target, delay, decimals) {
    setTimeout(() => {
      el.closest('.metric-stat').classList.add('metric-visible');
      let val = 0;
      const inc = target / (950 / 16);
      const t = setInterval(() => {
        val = Math.min(val + inc, target);
        el.textContent = (decimals ? val.toFixed(1) : Math.round(val)) + '%';
        if (val >= target) {
          el.textContent = target.toFixed(decimals ? 1 : 0) + '%';
          clearInterval(t);
        }
      }, 16);
    }, delay);
  }

  function initWorkPage() {
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
      entries.forEach(entry => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.add('visible');
          observer.unobserve(entry.target);

          // Trigger count-up when a chapter becomes visible
          if (entry.target.classList.contains('chapter')) {
            const n1 = entry.target.querySelector('#n1');
            const n2 = entry.target.querySelector('#n2');
            const n3 = entry.target.querySelector('#n3');
            if (n1 && n2 && n3) {
              countUp(n1, 90, 100, false);
              countUp(n2, 95, 320, false);
              countUp(n3, 17.4, 540, true);
            } else {
              // Non-numeric chapter — stagger-reveal the metrics
              entry.target.querySelectorAll('.metric-stat').forEach((stat, i) => {
                setTimeout(() => stat.classList.add('metric-visible'), 100 + i * 140);
              });
            }
          }
        }
      });
    }, { threshold: 0.05 });

    document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach(el => observer.observe(el));

    // Safety net — force all reveals visible after 3s
    setTimeout(() => {
      document.querySelectorAll('.reveal:not(.visible)').forEach(el => el.classList.add('visible'));
      document.querySelectorAll('.metric-stat:not(.metric-visible)').forEach(el => el.classList.add('metric-visible'));
    }, 3000);
  }

  document.addEventListener('astro:page-load', initWorkPage);
</script>

<style>
  /* ─── HERO ─── */
  .hero {
    padding: 160px 72px 80px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-label {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: var(--weight-light);
    font-size: var(--text-2xs);
    letter-spacing: 0.55em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.9s ease 0.1s forwards;
  }

  .hero-name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: var(--weight-semibold);
    font-size: clamp(72px, 12vw, 150px);
    line-height: 0.88;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-tight);
    color: var(--cream);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.9s ease 0.25s forwards;
  }

  .hero-name em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    display: block;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(17px, 2vw, 26px);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-top: 36px;
    max-width: 600px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.9s ease 0.5s forwards;
  }

  .hero-ghost {
    position: absolute;
    right: 40px;
    top: 110px;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: var(--weight-semibold);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(100px, 18vw, 200px);
    color: transparent;
    -webkit-text-stroke: 1px rgba(200,164,90,0.10);
    pointer-events: none;
    user-select: none;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeIn 1.4s ease 0.9s forwards;
  }

  /* ─── GOLD DIVIDER ─── */
  .gold-divider {
    width: 100%;
    overflow: visible;
    display: block;
    margin: 0;
    height: 48px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  /* ─── CHAPTER ─── */
  .chapter {
    max-width: 920px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 96px 72px 72px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .chapter-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  .chapter-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: var(--weight-light);
    font-size: clamp(56px, 8vw, 96px);
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-tight);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .chapter-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    font-size: var(--text-2xs);
    letter-spacing: 0.45em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .chapter-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: var(--weight-light);
    font-size: clamp(48px, 7vw, 88px);
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--cream);
    margin: 0 0 28px;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-tight);
  }

  .chapter-title em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--gold-light);
  }

  .chapter-hook {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(20px, 2.2vw, 26px);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--cream);
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 0 40px;
  }

  .chapter-rule {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(200, 164, 90, 0.4);
    margin: 0 0 40px;
    width: 80px;
  }

  .chapter-metrics {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 0;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .metric {
    padding: 0 28px;
  }

  .metric:first-child { padding-left: 0; }
  .metric:last-child  { padding-right: 0; }
  .metric + .metric   { border-left: 1px solid rgba(200, 164, 90, 0.18); }

  .metric-stat {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(8px);
    transition: opacity 0.5s ease, transform 0.5s ease;
  }

  .metric-stat.metric-visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  .metric-val {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: var(--weight-light);
    font-size: clamp(36px, 4.4vw, 52px);
    color: var(--gold);
    display: block;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }

  .metric-ba {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
  }

  .metric-ba-old   { text-decoration: line-through; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.4); }
  .metric-ba-arrow { color: var(--gold); }
  .metric-ba-new   { color: var(--gold-light); }
  .metric-ba-spacer { visibility: hidden; height: 1.4em; }

  .metric-lbl {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--cream);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    display: block;
  }

  .metric-context {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    display: block;
  }

  .chapter-read {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    color: var(--gold-light);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(226, 192, 122, 0.4);
    padding-bottom: 4px;
    transition: color 0.25s, border-color 0.25s;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .chapter-read:hover {
    color: var(--cream);
    border-color: var(--cream);
  }

  /* SKAI series tie-in inside chapter 02 */
  .chapter-aside {
    margin-top: 36px;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 1px dashed rgba(200, 164, 90, 0.25);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 14px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .chapter-aside-eyebrow {
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    font-size: var(--text-2xs);
    letter-spacing: 0.4em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .chapter-aside-link {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--gold-light);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(226, 192, 122, 0.35);
    padding-bottom: 2px;
    transition: color 0.25s, border-color 0.25s;
  }

  .chapter-aside-link:hover {
    color: var(--cream);
    border-color: var(--cream);
  }

  /* ─── CHAPTER BREAK ─── */
  .chapter-break {
    max-width: 920px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 72px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .chapter-break span {
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: rgba(200, 164, 90, 0.18);
  }

  .chapter-break .dot {
    flex: none;
    width: 5px;
    height: 5px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--gold);
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  /* ─── CTA ─── */
  .work-cta-section {
    max-width: 920px;
    margin: 80px auto 0;
    padding: 80px 72px 120px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .cta-label {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    font-size: var(--text-2xs);
    letter-spacing: 0.55em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .cta-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: var(--weight-light);
    font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 56px);
    line-height: var(--leading-snug);
    color: var(--cream);
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }

  .cta-heading em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--gold-light);
  }

  .work-cta {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    color: var(--gold-light);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(226, 192, 122, 0.4);
    padding-bottom: 4px;
    transition: color 0.25s, border-color 0.25s, letter-spacing 0.3s;
  }

  .work-cta:hover {
    color: var(--cream);
    border-color: var(--cream);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  /* ─── ANIMATIONS ─── */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(22px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; }
    to { opacity: 1; }
  }

  .reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(24px);
    transition: opacity 0.85s ease, transform 0.85s ease;
  }

  .reveal.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  /* ─── RESPONSIVE ─── */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hero,
    .work-cta-section,
    .chapter,
    .chapter-break {
      padding-left: 24px;
      padding-right: 24px;
    }

    .chapter { padding-top: 64px; padding-bottom: 48px; }

    .chapter-head { gap: 18px; }

    .chapter-metrics { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 24px; }
    .metric { padding: 0 0 24px; border-left: none !important; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(200, 164, 90, 0.18); }
    .metric:last-child { border-bottom: none; padding-bottom: 0; }
    .metric-ba-spacer { display: none; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .chapter-head { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 8px; }
    .chapter-num { font-size: 56px; }
    .chapter-title { font-size: 44px; }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .hero-label,
    .hero-name,
    .hero-sub,
    .hero-ghost {
      opacity: 1;
      animation: none;
    }
    .reveal { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
  }
</style>
</content>
</invoke>